1. *Plače* deca u učionici. (The children are crying in the classroom.)
2. Ona je *plakala* dok je gledala film. (She was crying while she was watching the movie.)
3. On *plače* od bola. (He is crying from pain.)
4. Ona *plače* od radosti. (She is crying from joy.)
5. *Plaču* njihove nesreće. (They are crying over their misfortune.)
6. Svi *plaču* na njegovoj sahrani. (Everyone is crying at his funeral.)
7. *Plačući* se vratila u kuću. (She returned home, crying.)
8. Videli smo ih *plačući* u zagrljaju. (We saw them crying in an embrace.)